items.title: Sarah Ferguson emails to Epstein show increasing desperation
items.description: The messages from the former Duchess of York appear to show her saying she feels "traumatised and alone".

items.title: Prince Edward says it's 'important' to remember victims as pressure on Andrew grows
items.description: The Duke of Edinburgh, Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor's brother, is the first senior royal to speak about the new documents.

items.title: Palace accused of 'messing' with McNeil mental health
items.description: Dwight McNeil's partner criticises Crystal Palace for "messing" with his mental health after the collapse of his transfer from Everton.

items.title: Light aircraft crashes 'with two on board'
items.description: A parachute canopy was later seen caught on a nearby pylon following the crash in Greater Manchester.

items.title: Rew century helps England to Under-19 World Cup final
items.description: Captain Thomas Rew makes a battling century as England book their place in the final of the Under-19 World Cup with a 27-run win over Australia.
